 of the modern age, to learn to live in a technological world without falling victim to the thrall of technological things.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aTechnologyxPhilosophy. 4aPhilosophy : Continental Philosophy. 7aRELIGION / Philosophy.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791482308423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791482308/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles